results.title: Dandelions blowing in the wind, bespoke wooden wall art sign with LIVE LOVE LAUGH. Handmade and hand painted shabby chic pallet style sign
results.description:
A bespoke  and custom plaque using a mixture of white wash and hazy blues for the background with  dandelions blowing in the wind. Finished with Live Love Laugh quote on the centre.

Made in "shabby chic" style with distressed timber slats and hand painted (No Vinyl or stencils) for that rustic long lasting look.

We can  make this sign in almost any size, just send us a message and we will do what we can to accommodate. We use a mixture or reclaimed and or pallet wood,  as well as distressing new timber, therefore it is impossible to duplicate a sign exactly. Due to using old pallet wood, there might be some non-structural cracks, knots and slight imperfections that give wonderful character to each sign. Every plaque is lovingly painted and sanded back to reveal some of the wood grain. We hand paint our wooden plaques with the typography wording and quotes. If you would like to personalise or change any wording you can do so 

For a bespoke service, please message any variations you would like at time of ordering. As each plaque is made to order, there will be slight variations in stain colour aswell as differences in the design and painting.

Make a lasting impression with our beautiful, thoughtful personalised keepsakes.

www.facebook.com/signsatsimplywood/
